title: Al Pacino Cafe
typeOfFood: Lacto, Pizza, Mediterranean, Take-out, Egyptian, BYOB, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. While menu is predominately meat based, there are a handful of things for vegetarians. Offers around three vegetarian sandwiches, and vegans can ask to leave out the cheese/dairy. Also a vegetable pizza and some salads. Generous portions. Very casual setting.
